      "data": {
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "tutorial-bootstrap-llm"
        },
        "markdown": "## Example handshake request\\n\\nAsk your model for **JSON only** and one tiny additive transaction. For example:\\n\\n```text\\nYou are being onboarded into a Twilite session.\\nComplete the handshake with JSON only, one additive transaction, one createNodes command, and one or two simple nodes that acknowledge readiness.\\n```\\n\\nA good handshake is small and boring. It proves the model can speak Twilite before you ask for anything bigger."
      }
    },
